ShippingPU_NOTE:
Orders selecting Standard Delivery will be shipped within 24 hours if the order is received Monday through Thursday by 1:00 PM EST for in-stock merchandise and pending credit card verification. Orders placed after 1:00 on Friday or on the weekend are processed the next business day.

Orders selecting Two Day or Next Day service will be shipped same day if the order is received Monday through Thursday before 1:00 PM EST; pending credit card verification for in-stock merchandise. Orders placed after 1:00 PM on Thursday or over the weekend are processed the next business day. Two Day and Next Day delivery options are only available within the continental United States excluding P.O. Boxes and Rural Routes.

Deliveries are made Monday through Friday, excluding holidays.

Fossil.com supports orders with delivery addresses within the United States, U.S. Territories, A.P.O./F.P.O. addresses, P.O. Boxes and Rural Routes. Only orders within the continental United States can be shipped Two Day or Next Day.

WorryFreePU_WORRY_FREE_DESC:
At Fossil.com we don't just stand behind our merchandise, we also do our best to provide a safe and convenient online shopping experience.

Fossil.com is a secure website. We utilize 128-bit, industry standard, encryption technologies to ensure that your credit card information is protected during a transaction. All transactions are screened for fraud via a third-party company called Cybersource (www.cybersource.com). We have implemented our own fraud database and every transaction that passes through our website is compared to our database to prevent fraudulent transactions from ever being completed.
